\c 8
\p
\v 1 Nenguva iyo ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha uchabvisa pamahwiro avo mapfupa amadzimambo avaJudha, namapfupa amachinda avo, namapfupa avapristi, namapfupa avaporofita, namapfupa avaigara paJerusarema;
\v 2 vachaaparadzira panopenya zuva nomwedzi nehondo yese yokudenga izvo zvavaida, nezvavaishumira, nezvavaitevera, nezvavaivinga, nezvavainamata; haangaunganidzwi, kana kuvigwa, asi achava mupfudze panyika.
\v 3 Rufu ruchasanangurwa kupfuura hupenyu navese vakasara panzvimbo dzese kwandakavadzingira ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo.
\s Kutsauka kwavanhu vaJehovha nokurohwa kwavo
\p
\v 4 Zvino unofanira kuti kwavari: Zvanzi naJehovha: Ko vanhu vangawa, vakasazomukazve here? Munhu ungatsauka, akasazodzoka here?
\v 5 Zvino vanhu ava veJerusarema vakadzokereiko nokudzokera kusingatongoperi? Vanonamatira kunyengera, vanoramba kudzoka.
\v 6 Ndakateerera, ndikanzwa, asi havana kutaura zvakarurama; hakuna munhu unochema kuipa kwake, achiti: Ndaiteiko? Umwe neumwe unotsauka nenzira yake, sebhiza rinomhanya kwazvo pakurwa.
\v 7 Zvirokwazvo, zimudo, riri kudenga, rinoziva nguva dzaro dzakatarwa, nenjiva nenyenganyenga nekondo dzinorangarira nguva yokuuya kwadzo, asi vanhu vangu havazivi murairo waJehovha.
\v 8 Munoreva seiko, muchiti: Takachenjera, murairo waJehovha tinawo? Asi tarirai, peni yenhema yavanyori inonyengera.
\v 9 Vanhu vakachenjera vakanyadziswa, vakavhunduka nokubatwa; tarirai, vakaramba shoko raJehovha, zvino vane njere dzakadiniko?
\v 10 Naizvozvo ndichapa vamwe vakadzi vavo, neminda yavo ndichaipa vamwe vachaiita yavo; nokuti umwe neumwe wavo, kubva kuvadiki kusvikira kuvakuru, umwe neumwe unokarira fuma; kubva kuvaporofita kusvikira kuvapristi umwe neumwe unoita nokunyengera.
\v 11 Vakangopodza vanga romukunda wavanhu vangu zvishoma, vachiti: Rugare, rugare! Izvo hakuna rugare.
\v 12 Ko vakanyadziswa nguva yavakaita zvinonyangadza here? Kwete, havana kutongonyara, vakakoniwa kucheneruka; naizvozvo vachawa pakati pavanowa; panguva yokurohwa kwavo vachagumburwa ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\v 13 Ndichavapedza chose, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha: Hakungavi namazambiringa pamuzambiringa, kana maonde pamuonde, namashizha achaoma ndakaraira vachavakukura.
\p
\v 14 Tinogarireiko pasi? Unganai, tipinde mumaguta akakomberedzwa, tifirepo; nokuti Jehovha Mwari wedu wakatiuraya, akatipa mvura inouraya kuti tiimwe; nokuti takatadzira Jehovha.
\v 15 Takange takatarira rugare, asi hakuna chakanaka chakasvika; takange takatarira nguva yokuporeswa, asi tarirai, takavhunduswa.
\v 16 Kufembedza kwamabhiza ake kwakanzwika achiri paDhani; nyika yese yakadedera nenzwi rokurira kwaane simba ake; nokuti asvika, apedza nyika nezvese zvirimo, neguta navese vageremo.
\v 17 Nokuti tarirai, ndichatuma pakati penyu nyoka nemvumbi, dzicharamba kuroyiwa; dzichakurumai, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\p
\v 18 Haiwa, dai ndaigona hangu kuzvinyaradza pakuchema kwangu! Moyo wangu waziya mukati mangu.
\v 19 Inzwai, inzwi rokuchema komukunda wavanhu vangu, rinobva kunyika iri kure-kure, richiti: Ko Jehovha haasi muZiyoni here? Mambo waro haasi mukati maro here? Vakanditsamwisireiko nezvifananidzo zvavo zvakavezwa, nezvavatorwa zvisina maturo?
\v 20 Kukohwa kwapera, zhizha rapfuura, asi tigere kuponeswa.
\v 21 Ini ndinokuvadzwa nokuda kokukuvadzwa komukunda wavanhu vangu; ndinochema, ndabatwa nokuvhunduswa.
\v 22 Ko hakuna muti webharisami muGiriyadhi here? Hakune n'angako here? Nokuti mukunda wavanhu vangu wakagoregerei kupodzwa?